counter = 0
fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 3, sharey=True, figsize = (12, 8))
for feat1 in person_features:
    for feat2 in person_features:
        if feat1 >= feat2:
            continue
        axes[counter / 3, counter % 3].scatter(sdata[feat1][labels == -1], sdata[feat2][labels == -1], c = 'red')
        axes[counter / 3, counter % 3].scatter(sdata[feat1][labels == 1], sdata[feat2][labels == 1], c = 'blue')
        axes[counter / 3, counter % 3].set_xlabel(feat1)
        axes[counter / 3, counter % 3].set_ylabel(feat2)
        counter += 1
